### Unconference Package tips ###

Setup your project by new project -> package with

Learn how to use "usethis" package.
Roxygen2 is amazing for skeletoning documentation. Click on function, then the code toolbar, insert roxygen skeleton.
Once you fill this out, use devtools::document() to copy these changes to a documentation page inside the man folder.

Usethis::use_package() is a great function for adding dependancies to a package without needing to do anything.

usethis::use_readme_rmd() to insert an rmarkdown readme file.
